      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="6112827f-f250-47bf-884b-fea06829d390" type="Determiner">
          <Vi>mỗi, mọi</Vi>
          <En>used to refer to all members of a group without exception; used before a singular noun to mean 'each and without exception'</En>
          <Example>Every student must submit their assignment by Friday.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="43086604-0a25-4cb2-9499-b99cf0119446">
              <Vi>Được dùng để nhấn mạnh tính toàn bộ, không loại trừ cá thể nào trong một tập hợp.</Vi>
              <En>Used to emphasize inclusion of all individuals in a group, with no exceptions.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="d9ff27eb-dcf6-4120-ac37-894efd27579c">
              <Vi>Trong ngữ cảnh lặp lại thường xuyên, như "mỗi ngày", "mỗi tuần".</Vi>
              <En>In contexts of regular repetition, such as "every day", "every week".</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
        </Meaning>
      </Meanings>
